-----------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to assign a maximum value of an integer in java, use below

int max = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
int min = Integer.MIN_VALUE;

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To remove a pair from hashmap use the below code

map.remove(key);

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Generic rules to identify sliding window problem

1. An Array or String should be given
2. Ask about sub array or sub string
3. Given K (for a fixed length sliding window problem)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To find the power of a number, use below

Math.pow(2,3);

The above line will calculate 2 power three

